Scope：
The app is designed for patients, children, and elderly with mild to moderate medication or supplement needs.
It allows users to create, view, and edit their daily Medicine / Supplement plans.
It allows reminders and notifications for scheduled intake.
It allows to record history of Medicine / Supplement usage for user review.
It allows to help users maintain a healthy habit of taking Medicine / Supplement on time.

Out of Scope：
NO prescribe medication.
NO provide professional medical advice.
NO offer online medical consultations.
NO store or process non-medical information.
NO intended for commercial purposes or third-party profit.
It cannot replace a doctor or caregiver.

Constraints：
App must run on smartphones or tablets with notification support.
Users must register and log in to access full features.
All reminders and records must access device’s system time.
Data storage is limited to the user’s account.
Users must be responsible for correct input of dosage and schedules.
